{"tid":2479250,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"緬甸軍政府無限期禁用流動網絡　抗爭民衆已經轉用無線電","createTime":"2021-04-07T16:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T16:33:40.000Z","uid":261647,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"397567d67795b2cf1e386c8e2823a826e704dda1","tid":2479250,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:30:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/04/02/myanmar-military-internet-shutdown-bloodbath/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F04%2F02%2Fmyanmar-military-internet-shutdown-bloodbath%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYYHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=0ac01251\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/04/02/myanmar-military-internet-shutdown-bloodbath/fun-tech/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/download.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2Fdownload.png&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYYHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=bdaf0f85\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/download.png</a><br />\n<br />\n緬甸局勢越發緊張，軍政府對於網絡的控制也越來越嚴格，除了之前的晚間斷網措施之外，最近更下令今日開始無限期禁用流動網絡上網，直到另行通知為止。<br />\n<br />\n據國際電訊商 Ooredoo 的消息指，緬甸軍政府已經向當地電訊商下令停止在國內提供無線網絡服務，也就是說只有固網光纖網絡或者衛星網絡可以繼續使用，而這樣的服務在緬甸並不普及，意味着大部分緬甸民衆將會失去戶外連線能力。<br />\n<br />\n據稱緬甸抗爭民衆已經轉用無線電、離線網上資源和短訊來彼此聯絡，嘗試找出新的出路。對於緬甸民衆而言，斷網措施令他們更難與外界聯絡，分享當地所發生事件的記錄，而駐守當地的國際媒體亦需要另外想辦法來進行深入報導。"},{"pid":"1d548b03cc941caf731a22cc2098538bf2c5a540","tid":2479250,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:31:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/04/02/myanmar-military-internet-shutdown-bloodbath/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F04%2F02%2Fmyanmar-military-internet-shutdown-bloodbath%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYYHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=0ac01251\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/04/02/myanmar-military-internet-shutdown-bloodbath/fun-tech/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/download.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2Fdownload.png&h=2dd40fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n緬甸局勢越發緊張，軍政府對於網絡的控制也越來越嚴格，除了之前的晚間斷網措施之外，最近更下令今日開始無限期禁用流動網絡上網，直到另行通知為止。<br />\n<br />\n據國際電訊商 Ooredoo 的消息指，緬甸軍政府已經向當地電訊商下令停止在國內提供無線網絡服務，也就是說只有固網光纖網絡或者衛星網絡可以繼續使用，而這樣的服務在緬甸並不普及，意味着大部分緬甸民衆將會失去戶外連線能力。<br />\n<br />\n據稱緬甸抗爭民衆已經轉用無線電、離線網上資源和短訊來彼此聯絡，嘗試找出新的出路。對於緬甸民衆而言，斷網措施令他們更難與外界聯絡，分享當地所發生事件的記錄，而駐守當地的國際媒體亦需要另外想辦法來進行深入報導。"},{"pid":"2ad443054c6ac28c0704a18989d15dceed02bf19","tid":2479250,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:32:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://j.gifs.com/OMVEKQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.gifs.com%2FOMVEKQ.gif&h=8d743361&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a56578ffb75e619865051110968f6068efb7c0c","tid":2479250,"uid":264974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:33:40.000Z","msg":"The world needs starlink"}]}